It's an informative trailer. Here's what I glean. In season 10, Larry will be annoyed by some everyday minutiae. He will make people angry. Some of the angry people will know him well; others will be strangers. He will be asked to leave a lot of houses. Susie will curse at him. And some famous actors will play themselves.

No sarcasm: I can't wait. This show has been a reason to stay alive in the first two decades of the 21st century. Never change, Curb.
